menu "Main Application Configuration"

    config ENABLE_LED_LIGHT
        bool "Enable LED Light Module"
        default y
        help
            Enable or disable the LED light module.
            When enabled, LED light functionality will be available.
            When disabled, LED light module will not be compiled.

    config ENABLE_RGB_LIGHT
        bool "Enable RGB Light Module"
        default y
        help
            Enable or disable the RGB light module.
            When enabled, RGB light functionality will be available.
            When disabled, RGB light module will not be compiled.

endmenu